http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/Two-die-in-accident/article14025894.ece

Two youths died on the spot when a vehicle hit their motorcycle near Baba Cross on the outskirts of Sandur town on Thursday morning.The police gave their name as Mallikarjun (28) and Chandrashekar (22), who are siblings, of Krishnanagar area.According to police, Mallikarjun was going by his newly purchased bike to a dargah, when an unidentified vehicle knocked them down.When the Sandur police tried to shift the bodies to a hospital, the parents of the youth and local residents objected to it. The police pacified them and shifted the bodies.